#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_cover
msgid "<b>Bringing life to your interior</b>"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_title
msgid "<b>Everything is designed.<br/> Few things are designed well.</b>"
msgstr "<b>Alt er designet.<br/> Få ting er designet godt.</b>"

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_cover
msgid "Discover More"
msgstr "Få mere at vide"

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_cover
msgid "Discover our unique pieces of furniture selected for you."
msgstr "Oplev vores unikke møbler, som vi har udvalgt specielt til dig."

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Every week our shop receive new products. Some are only on sale for a "
"limited period of time."
msgstr ""
"Hver uge får du nye produkter i vores butik. Nogle af dem er kun "
"tilgængelige i en begrænset periode."

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_three_columns
msgid "For the whole Family"
msgstr "For hele familien"

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_banner
msgid ""
"Our products are designed for small to medium size companies willing to "
"optimize their performance."
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_call_to_action
msgid "Our services"
msgstr "Vores serviceydelser"

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_three_columns
msgid "Tailored advice"
msgstr "Skræddersyet rådgivning"

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_banner
msgid "The art of Design"
msgstr ""

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model:ir.model,name:theme_loftspace.model_theme_utils
msgid "Theme Utils"
msgstr "Designværktøjer"

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"To buy unique pieces is to buy a piece of the artist: His passion put in the"
" execution of the object, his hours of reflexion, his dexterity... It is a "
"committed, ethical act, which encourages a responsible and direct economy."
msgstr ""
"At købe unikke værker er at købe et stykke af kunstneren: Den passion, der "
"er lagt i værket, de mange timers overvejelser og den håndværksmæssige "
"kunnen. Det er en engageret og etisk handling, der fremmer en ansvarlig og "
"direkte økonomi."

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_three_columns
msgid "Unique Items"
msgstr "Unikke varer"

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_three_columns
msgid ""
"Whether it is to help you see clearly in a project, to confirm a choice or "
"when you have no idea about the layout of your interior, our advisers are "
"there to accompany you throughout your project."
msgstr ""
"Uanset om du har brug for hjælp til at få overblik over et projekt, bekræfte "
"et valg eller er i tvivl om, hvordan du skal indrette dit hjem, står vores "
"rådgivere klar til at hjælpe dig gennem hele processen."

#. module: theme_loftspace
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_loftspace.s_call_to_action
msgid "Would you like more information <br/>about a product?"
msgstr "Har du brug for yderligere oplysninger <br/>om et produkt?"
